        <h1>Weight Gain Plan (18-25 Underweight)</h1>

        <h2>Diet Plan (Weekly Variation)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Oatmeal with nuts, banana, and full-fat milk</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken, rice, vegetables, and avocado</td>
                <td>Peanut butter sandwich with honey</td>
                <td>Salmon, quinoa, smoothie with yogurt and berries</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Scrambled eggs with cheese, whole wheat toast, and orange juice</td>
                <td>Lean beef with mashed potatoes and steamed greens</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with granola and nuts</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with brown rice and vegetables</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Avocado toast with boiled eggs and a glass of milk</td>
                <td>Grilled salmon with couscous and sautéed spinach</td>
                <td>Protein shake with almonds</td>
                <td>Pasta with ground turkey and cheese</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Chia seed pudding with nuts and berries</td>
                <td>Grilled shrimp with quinoa and avocado salad</td>
                <td>Cottage cheese with mixed fruits</td>
                <td>Stir-fried tofu with brown rice and steamed broccoli</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Protein smoothie (banana, almond milk, protein powder)</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with pasta and olive oil dressing</td>
                <td>Handful of walnuts and peanut butter toast</td>
                <td>Beef stew with potatoes and vegetables</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Omelet with cheese, whole wheat bread, and a smoothie</td>
                <td>Turkey and avocado wrap with whole wheat tortilla</td>
                <td>Cashews and a glass of milk</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with rice and steamed carrots</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Boiled eggs with whole wheat toast and peanut butter</td>
                <td>Vegetable stir-fry with tofu and brown rice</td>
                <td>Protein bar and yogurt</td>
                <td>Grilled steak with mashed sweet potatoes</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h2>Gym Routine (Optimized for Muscle Gain)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Workout</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Upper Body: Bench press, pull-ups, shoulder press, bicep curls)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Lower Body: Squats, lunges, deadlifts, calf raises)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Rest or Active Recovery (light walking, stretching, yoga)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Full-Body: Deadlifts, rows, dips, leg press)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Core & Functional: Planks, hanging leg raises, farmer’s walk, sled push)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Optional: Low-intensity cardio or bodyweight exercises</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Rest or Recovery</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
